<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yswʿ wḥdh ḥwy̱</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- yasūʿu waḥ̊dahu ḥaway̱
 jamīʿa ạảẘṣāfi ạl̊kamāl̊
 wah̊wa ạl̊ʿajību fī ạl̊bahā
 wāl̊ʿizĩ ạảẙḍaⁿạ wāl̊jalạl̊

[V2]
 2- hadẖā hūa rā̊̉su ạl̊jasad̊
 wah̊wa ʿalay̱ ạl̊kulĩ ạr̊tafaʿ̊
 yasūʿu waḥ̊dahu lahu
 ạlsũl̊ṭānu ạảẙḍaⁿạ qad̊ dufiʿ̊

[V3]
 3- fāảyũ sẖakẖ̊ṣiⁿ yā turay̱
 naẓīru sẖakẖ̊ṣihi ạl̊munīr̊
 famā lahu baẙna ạl̊waray̱
 ạảẘ fī ạlsãmāwāti naẓīr̊

[V4]
 4- laẙsa lanā mūsay̱ ại̹dẖaⁿạ
 walạ ại̹ylīãạ maʿahu
 las̊nā nurīdu ạản̊ naray̱
 ại̹lạã yasūʿa waḥ̊dahu</lyrics>
</song>